Package aima.gui.swing.applications.search.games

Class FifteenPuzzleApp

  • java.lang.Object
    • aima.gui.swing.framework.SimpleAgentApp
      • aima.gui.swing.applications.search.games.FifteenPuzzleApp
  • public class FifteenPuzzleApp
extends SimpleAgentApp
    Graphical 15-puzzle game application. It demonstrates the performance of different search algorithms. Additionally, users can make experiences with human problem solving.
    Author:
    Ruediger Lunde, M. Kaan Tasbas
